The '''Interplanetary Charts and Surveys''' was a scout organization which was affected when the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] made cut-backs to exploration during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], forcing [[Jowart Typok]] among others to leave.

